{"tid":1762888,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：撤撥款因尊重議員 政府資源運用必有政治操作","createTime":"2019-11-30T02:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T04:17:58.000Z","uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9f74f6adf90f78552fcd40c09c3bc273cdb8ae28","tid":1762888,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:22:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495264-20191130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495264-20191130.htm&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4jsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=17c86b2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495264-20191130.htm&h=a425db59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495264-20191130.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府早前撤回涉及3間大學的撥款申請，教育局局長楊潤雄在本台節目《星期六問責》表示，暫撤撥款是因為有議員有關注，政府亦須尊重。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有建制派批評指，撥款予大學會助長示威活動，有關說法是否政府凌駕教育或民生，楊潤雄指，政治不應進入校園的意思，是不應在校園內進行政治活動，亦不希望政治凌駕教育專業，但他承認政府的資源如何運用，是需要由不同人士給予意見，政府最終如何調撥資源一定涉及政治操作。"},{"pid":"f78288b39c8b3201295aafc3ff7e3c8b58abba92","tid":1762888,"uid":8441,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"又話政治唔應該影響民生項目既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fe1f82ab99c53762e4d51bc42cb19e3046727b","tid":1762888,"uid":180716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:29:45.000Z","msg":"佢知唔知自己講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚矛盾喎大佬"},{"pid":"fd59a4a5712ecc045af01787c3641597f8009282","tid":1762888,"uid":42740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:31:56.000Z","msg":"又話唔好政治化 而家又政治操作<br />\n你老母閪啦"},{"pid":"8c797a8ee1fd774c100d9b5119d933e9fdecb892","tid":1762888,"uid":13149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"點撚樣呀 彈出彈入你講哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/n